Description: Agreement with Lehman Brothers dated 8/08/2006 to pay 2.87% per year times the notional amount. In exchange for that periodic payment, upon a default event by Station Casinos, Inc., Lehman Brothers agrees to pay the Portfolio the notional amount of the swaps. To receive that payment, the portfolio must deliver a bond (with par value equal to the notional amount of the swap issued by Stations Casinos, Inc, to Lehman Brothers.
